{"tid":311312,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 各大交友平台 / 交友 apps","createTime":"2017-07-06T13:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T14:54:40.000Z","uid":123308,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cee0d96e0b797040c2919f084626c0d28fcade86","tid":311312,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:42:32.000Z","msg":"網上有相關 post，但都有一段歷史，加上呢度冇，係時候再整合再整過個新列表<br />\n<br />\n交友平台，由舊到新排列：<br />\n<br />\n&gt; 緣份配對計劃- Match Up<br />\n已摺埋，但個網寫住「開發人員正在更新全新計劃!」）<br />\n<br />\n&gt; www.hkg-match.ga<br />\n已摺埋<br />\n<br />\n&gt; Skylight<br />\n已摺埋，當時僅限香港 UGC 八大 + SYU + OUHK<br />\n<br />\n&gt; 緣份相遇計劃- Triangel<br />\n運行中，呢度有相關 post<br />\n<br />\n&gt; 緣份。相遇 &ndash; Nextravel<br />\n運行中，呢度有相關 post<br />\n<br />\n頭四個平台主要玩法係用文字打 CV，幾日時間畀你揀人，睇人地 CV，然後交換 contact，但當然唔包生仔<br />\n<br />\n最後嗰個如冇理解錯，應該係撞三個號碼，睇下人地揀唔揀中你 set 個 number，中就交換 contact<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n輪到交友 apps<br />\n<br />\nMade in Hong Kong：<br />\n<br />\n&gt; MaskOFF<br />\n背後公司應該係 Richard Li 嘅 Stakk。<br />\n玩法同 Tinder 個啲唔同，都幾特別，就係用聲音嚟溝通，可以留 voice message，又可以「打限時 5 分鐘電話」畀對方，打完電話代表過咗一個關卡，可以進入另一 stage，例如開 camera FaceTime 講嘢，不過塊面會遮住 (AR)，最後關頭先會見到真正 face to face<br />\n<br />\n以下應該係香港製造，但基本上唔多活躍：<br />\n&gt; My Cup of Tea<br />\n&gt; 2Date<br />\n&gt; ECFriend<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\nMade in the USA（好似係）<br />\n<br />\n&gt; Tinder<br />\n呢個唔駛講啦，睇 Google Play Store 個下載次數就知全世界最多人用，香港都唔例外<br />\n<br />\n&gt; OkCupid<br />\n玩之前要填一啲關於你嘅個人喜好，然後先可以玩。<br />\n每個男仔／女仔都會由系統對比你所填嘅答案，計到你同你個男仔／女仔究竟幾多 % 相似。<br />\n同 Tinder 玩法差唔多，但唔似 Tinder 要大家 match 咗先可以講嘢<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <a href=\"http://Match.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMatch.com&d=r624e6JfBadnJJUekWgyGPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6cbdd67f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Match.com</a><br />\n1995 年就開站，香港都有個官方網站，但其實香港冇乜人用<br />\n<br />\n以上三個 apps 都係出自同一間公司叫「IAC」<br />\n<br />\n&gt; Happn<br />\n玩法同上面啲 apps 有啲唔同，就係 app 入面你見到嘅人，就係你現實生活同你擦身而過嘅人，用 GPS 計算。個 pool 多唔多人視乎你多唔多去一啲人多嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n&gt; Skout<br />\n呢個唔駛講啦都，出名多狗公，龍蛇混雜。<br />\n同樣同 Tinder 玩法差唔多，但唔似 Tinder 要大家 match 咗先可以講嘢<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <a href=\"http://Lovestruck.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FLovestruck.com&d=r624e6JfBadnJJUekWgyGPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=35e1e0c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Lovestruck.com</a><br />\n地鐵、電車都賣過唔少廣告，玩得嘅多數係以結婚為目標，不過好似要課金<br />\n<br />\n&gt; Coffee Meets Bagel<br />\n英文唔好嘅話可以 skip，多（偽）ABC<br />\n<br />\n&gt; Badoo<br />\n&gt; Hot or Not<br />\n擺佢哋喺一齊係因為其實表面上係兩個 apps，但背後同一個 database，基本上用是但一個就等於用埋另一個。<br />\n香港一般常用，多 MK 妹，賓賓都唔少<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\nMade in Singapore<br />\n<br />\n&gt; LunchClick<br />\n玩得嘅多數係以結婚為目標，要玩要身份認證，以約會為主調，不過搞到咁，當然要課金，$45x 港紙一個月，或者 $17x 一個月，但要畀足 12 個月月費<br />\n<br />\n&gt; eSynchrony<br />\n同樣，玩得嘅多數係以結婚為目標，要玩要身份認證，畢業證書，乜乜證書&hellip;&hellip;要答好多問題，大約個幾星期後會有佢哋篩選過嘅對象畀你。同樣，又係同上一樣，請課金 please<br />\n<br />\n以上兩個 apps 出自同一公司 Lunch Actually 手筆<br />\n<br />\n&gt; Paktor<br />\n想溝新加坡仔仔／女女，呢個 app 就啱你，因為好少香港人<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\nMade in Thailand<br />\n<br />\n&gt; Noonswoon<br />\n同樣以結婚為目標，課金好似要六百幾七百港紙，應該係以年計<br />\n<br />\n以上個 app 被香港公司 DateTix 收購咗，source:<br />\n&gt; 促成15對情人，泰國約會應用Noonswoon被香港競爭對手Datetix收購: <a href=\"http://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1221355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hksilicon.com%2Farticles%2F1221355&d=r624e6JfBadnJJUekWgyGPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=834343c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1221355</a><br />\n&gt; 金風玉露點相逢？DateTix搭橋鋪路吸金: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20160524/bkn-20160524121949891-0524_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20160524%2Fbkn-20160524121949891-0524_00842_001.html&d=r624e6JfBadnJJUekWgyGPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=9a69a734\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20160524/bkn-20160524121949891-0524_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\nMade in 台灣類：<br />\n<br />\n&gt; WeTouch<br />\n對象係大學生，香港一般常用，台灣本土當然較多。&rsquo;Freemium&rsquo;，進階功能先要課金，免費都用得<br />\n<br />\n&gt; iPair<br />\n對象係大學生至中女。都有唔少賓賓，系統有時又會整啲一睇就知係台灣／假嘅 profile picture，令你覺得有人 match 你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，繼而叫你課金解鎖解功能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。想傾計就必先盛惠 $17x / month，不過相信唔會有人想畀 $17x 同賓賓交友<br />\n<br />\n&gt; SweetRing<br />\n對象係要結婚嘅人，相對比較少「假人」。但同樣，同想傾計嘅話，請先盛惠 ~$500，一畀要畀 3 個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，仲貴過 Tinder 或者其他出名啲嘅交友 apps<br />\n<br />\n而上面呢三個台灣 apps 都係出自同一間公司，source：<br />\n&gt; 愛情公寓止跌回升！婚戀交友app「SweetRing」成營收成長主力: <a href=\"https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/39177/BN-2016-04-11-145414-44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnext.com.tw%2Farticle%2F39177%2FBN-2016-04-11-145414-44&d=r624e6JfBadnJJUekWgyGPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=3f9478e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/39177/BN-2016-04-11-145414-44</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位巴打絲打補完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，大家集思廣益 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92d7cdd47b6c861ed382880dd26e09f5a4e2d9b","tid":311312,"uid":8728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574714344616fa4c58abc984b842c3996ee41e49","tid":311312,"uid":43308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:41:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"191a693f7f59d277d71702731848662727c4206e","tid":311312,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"留低負或正評嘅都可以講吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3684887550a73e59823c72371bd1f6039a34459a","tid":311312,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"或者各位有冇咩心得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930d389da04668b97c40761bf731b0d656199349","tid":311312,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:02:28.000Z","msg":"推下先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d720fa939c4ae1d5d71a523c7291c4f8d0ae59","tid":311312,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T15:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68b51a232435552ce4b3aacbaaa9c8531085aa1","tid":311312,"uid":60817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T15:24:22.000Z","msg":"玩過SayHi,tinder,skout ,coffee meet bagel<br />\nSayHi,普遍上左年紀先玩，玩左冇耐冇玩<br />\nSkout,好多東南亞人，雞，同mk,靚女唔會show 你<br />\nCoffee meet bagel, 一日得9個機會，唔課金好難match,課金又貴。普遍D人質素好D，正常D.<br />\nTinder, 多人玩，D人正常D，多ABC, 呢個App算最好，係難match"},{"pid":"bcc1c6c88d52747dcc6306812d42d9674d101e92","tid":311312,"uid":60817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T15:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩過SayHi,tinder,skout ,coffee meet bagel<br />\nSayHi,普遍上左年紀先玩，玩左冇耐冇玩<br />\nSkout,好多東南亞人，雞，同mk,靚女唔會show 你<br />\nCoffee meet bagel, 一日得9個機會，唔課金好難match,課金又貴。普遍D人質素好D，正常D.<br />\nTinder, 多人玩，D人正常D，多ABC, 呢個App算最好，係難match</blockquote><br />\n玩得呢D真係唔可以太認真，當比個機會自己識吓人算"},{"pid":"c80a17c120448061518047dcf5b6907331ff6bce","tid":311312,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:44:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩過SayHi,tinder,skout ,coffee meet bagel<br />\nSayHi,普遍上左年紀先玩，玩左冇耐冇玩<br />\nSkout,好多東南亞人，雞，同mk,靚女唔會show 你<br />\nCoffee meet bagel, 一日得9個機會，唔課金好難match,課金又貴。普遍D人質素好D，正常D.<br />\nTinder, 多人玩，D人正常D，多ABC, 呢個App算最好，係難match</blockquote><br />\n多謝分享 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下星期 Tinder 又好似出新功能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5194078f5c6f238f4